    This interface is a Listener for the addHabitEvent dialog, it is used so that when the user presses the create or cancel button, the calling activity can be informed and take appropriate action

    This interface is a Listener for the editHabitEvent dialog, it is used so that when the user presses the create or cancel button, the calling activity can be informed and take appropriate action
    OnFollowRequestListener
    This interface is created so that upon occurence of a follow request appropriate aciton can be taken

    This interface is created so that appropriate action can be taken when a habit is viewed
